 commands for getCommandName.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03ade9410003a0660169f118c1232481938eb8b7021fa367f7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8RjNAfnCsspD3fwgs5GGS2vtzkUimXOBebYlF-o2csm_5-LGE41hBhBIBF2Vw72qhOEyGOjQ9Jq_CgeNeL5_hgHMUH23zkAvpbZn9tPuqvifEuOsog80_Cr9KGaUrLx7QpCLhSGuJQdJ2-Ni2BndtdhmH2iR_84DPtzejsHsH-TMuGmPELTMO-ulkPE6LCv2btgImDTctHCwmIfQdlvIQVdObgBeKoHwNfW2otGZQ2Gf0NQoqd_olyyjrc9El2feBW14pa8YwJIh_5Xg7VdaT0pm7SECTQBaxitGS1JXsBhaWHnh7nFB0VYTytqX4DksY5MpmUfk4GgLjiz4xKrfwh0UOYSqhMz4TdJGnPIX4V1Z0t1hqrTDSvSRKhvNhApU5cY6rfLEA6uR47MKzcUbw_Paubn0Z5HzLRTyGWxQymDnXWiqx6YnihqgIoglLePjfXiXEQ_Ehak1i15olf043niMB9p0jjq6I3qKjN_k8ge6RZTyjQ0Rn8PaAQTqv0cFQRxuSTmfUin3-u3IOx8XgocG9l6XavGvWSuA7znwSZF7ZakChukhupbc0TyMRls91xPbNvnxoRqxdDrNtXjPwVpeu9W_lzoA_azS5pQafpPgN_uYnnlivAFB81zTzzTmem5iwMlaYvPMkjU12ql6eJMf3PReXH7jTmyJGqrKTW2GAsciIsWSqhSF6c7lo8V7jWBuqRHxKfEEtsAjyCc07wDAz2YH2YLUca1SJggEjOBbag40RqLWdyMuaeu_9WIYO9DaZY7-uuhLsfm5dUYhdWspli_guJPTgjpc6XgsT2omXwpIam_i82GOjFn97hBs5s-q_yQsT87e2Skyc6ICeVquhXwPNLU3ecsZPkflKC4XaYeKRi64g8i6-zmiWwFZ0tyzkNAfWAkwvrt9Qp8lYc64GZtWzCrfmpXZG9z_81oXIBRxrJsMJ9nH9bW-mLEazWPVxdEheDLHNm-6jMT71xyXP_e6R_sbAXl2iqiZ_c_XtL4cjYnlTCHrdfDx0izKCWBh8rmFQZPEf8Ks3ug_U-5UlBXFjIObK0GPdcZdkfwGfsemEGhFNhrSChN2sQNG4a0CA6VV_99z_29AGkAdXyKxK1DMC4E4SUMTNXdSVGb602b8tVhktFf-ir1YCPt-PYklqGZxMsy3YAUf2F-2ZglHqb2yE7XwYzS5fFb0NFgXqHWkbyvg1U2LJ6lMcB_2up1Fs6iCO5X9pzlth5TZJEIw0dx5_W-lWNH2YGd8NnXOgYoj1OFh1ITuv6IKr-9nPuCYb9F88o2n0woYDUm0sIjv0TEm0llaRD-8KcjuhyEx2x6NTJmPxGa0ewIlCHz1fJk6sUJCDHPOPod5y9XyUuJ9GP8T5Cm8MScUYLZf1EQKMR-0DiZ_24eQfJUaZq1sk974Tq4n8Pm48RRMb66g5z_wkKmVvnLarPIyzZNLIsxULPgsquZQwJHibd4a5eeQfOj2HEGZqLIKElIzFjeGczKRgixmANWOpdE7GLFMYEzqhTBKhBkVuM5qNGbKotCTnXoIxtdZbvONHi5JHI7woswF6IPSQfWbo1z_IXlZoztJjzNY1SXB9AB3a7zxzfpecGCfhX9MlyKRWs8GmzdBl_uSRH34-dLfuRcMfoNZEtpLcfwoW_t-Obk3p1dbFMPyX7QOvCD34Hl-xXnZAhxjfd2JdUWv1XtGC5u375UpKc_WTEfGquGphjy7FpIz8oFCSt8bBcXQqNe-zJh78AC3zRW98mi0pzq9xu626qEacq7ruPbN2dh-KcT-fUtyrO2AsVYdq_MpoyIx4vJMSKq9AyPrgKsOTSS_f